<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <title>Privacy Policy — Ami Steelman</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=Space+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --slate-deep: #1C2B3A;
      --slate-mid: #3D5A6B;
      --steel: #5B8FA8;
      --fog: #A8BCC8;
      --ice: #E8EEF2;
      --ink: #1C2B3A;
      --ink-secondary: #3D5A6B;
      --ink-tertiary: #7A96A6;
      --surface: #F4F7F9;
      --rule: #D6E2E9;
      --white: #ffffff;
    }

    html { font-size: 16px; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.8;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .site-name {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--ink);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .site-name span {
      color: var(--steel);
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    main {
      padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
    }

    .page-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--steel);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.75rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .updated {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-left: 2px solid var(--steel);
      background: rgba(91, 143, 168, 0.06);
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      padding-top: 2.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    section:first-of-type h2 {
      border-top: none;
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    p {
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
    }

    ul li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      padding: 0.4rem 0 0.4rem 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    ul li::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--steel);
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .app-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--slate-mid);
      background: rgba(91, 143, 168, 0.1);
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin-right: 0.4rem;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .contact-block {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .contact-block p {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contact-block a {
      color: var(--steel);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .contact-block a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 2rem 0;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      background: var(--white);
    }

    footer .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
      main { padding: 2.5rem 0 4rem; }
      footer .container { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="site-name">ami<span>steelman</span></a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container">

      <p class="page-label">// legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <p class="intro">
        I build small tools and apps as an independent developer. This policy covers all apps and add-ons published by Ami Steelman at amisteelman.com. I keep things simple: your data stays yours, and I don't collect what I don't need.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2>Who this covers</h2>
        <p>This policy applies to all apps, add-ons, and tools published by Ami Steelman, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="app-tag">Google Workspace</span> FontSwap — font scanning and replacement for Google Slides &amp; Docs</li>
          <li>Any future apps or tools published under amisteelman.com</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>What my apps access</h2>
        <p>Each app only requests access to what it genuinely needs to function. For Google Workspace add-ons like FontSwap:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Font family names and text style metadata within your open document</li>
          <li>The ability to modify text styles in your document (to perform replacements)</li>
          <li>Your document's UI context (to display the add-on dialog)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This access is used solely to perform the operation you request — scanning or replacing fonts — within your current session.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>What I do not do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>I do not store, log, or retain any of your document content</li>
          <li>I do not transmit your data to any external server</li>
          <li>I do not sell, share, or trade your data with third parties</li>
          <li>I do not use your data for advertising or analytics</li>
          <li>I do not retain any information between sessions</li>
        </ul>
        <p>All processing happens locally within Google's infrastructure during your active session. When you close the add-on, nothing is kept.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>My Google Workspace add-ons run entirely within Google's Apps Script platform and are subject to <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" style="color: var(--steel);">Google's Privacy Policy</a>. I do not integrate any additional third-party analytics, tracking, or data services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>My apps are not directed at children under 13 and I do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>If I add new apps that handle data differently, I will update this page and revise the "Last updated" date above. Continued use of my apps after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="contact-block">
        <p style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Questions or concerns?</p>
        <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how your data is handled, please reach out:</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:privacy@amisteelman.com">privacy@amisteelman.com</a></p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">I'm a solo developer and will respond personally.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <span>© 2026 Ami Steelman</span>
      <a href="/">amisteelman.com</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>

